    <briefdescription>
<para>Minimum supported connection interval group. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Each group represents an arithmetic sequence of supported connection intervals: min, min + stride, min + 2 * stride, ..., min + n * stride (where min + n * stride &lt;= max)</para>
<para>Example: min = 10 (1250 us), max = 60 (7500 us), stride = 5 (625 us) -&gt; Supported: 1250 us, 1875 us, 2500 us, ..., 6875 us, 7500 us </para>
    </detaileddescription>
